  <section xml:id="ex2-8"><title><xref ref="ch2-8"/></title>
    <exercises>
      <exercise>
      Determine whether each of the following equations are exact. If it
      is exact, find the solution. Implicit solutions are fine.
      <ol>
      <li><m>\left(2x+3\right)+\left(2y-2\right)y^{\prime}=0}</m></li>
      <li> <m>\left(2x+4y\right)+\left(2x-2y\right)y^{\prime}=0}</m></li>
      <li> <m>\left(3x^{2}-2xy+2\right)dx+\left(6y^{2}-x^{2}+3\right)dy=0</m></li>
      <li> <m>\left(2xy^{2}+2y\right)+\left(2x^{2}y+2x\right)y^{\prime}=0}</m></li>
